      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんを部屋に残してきたけど\nスリクスの三人とちゃんと交流出来てるかな……",
      "startTime": 3.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3866.6666667000004,
          "startTime": 7.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、いいお湯だったわ……あら？",
      "startTime": 8.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、遙子さん。お風呂に行ってたんですか？",
      "startTime": 14.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、みんなと一緒に温泉に入ってたのよ",
      "startTime": 17.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですか\nスリクスとお風呂に入るなんて随分打ち解けましたね",
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あれは打ち解けたと言っていいのかしら……",
      "startTime": 27.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どんな様子だったんですか？",
      "startTime": 31.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "どんな様子と言われても……そうねぇ……",
      "startTime": 33.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6800.000000000005,
          "startTime": 40.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ～、極楽極楽～",
      "startTime": 41.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 33.33333329999988,
          "startTime": 41.4
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1033.3333332999998,
          "startTime": 42.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "極楽気分で顔が溶けちゃいそう。こんな緩んだ顔\n{user}君には見せられないわね～",
      "startTime": 50.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　温泉の成分と効能が書いてあるわ\nちょっとレポーターの練習でもしちゃおうかしら",
      "startTime": 59.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 54.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "「今日は美肌の湯で有名な温泉にやって来ました～\n泉質は、無色透明のナトリウム炭酸水素塩泉です」",
      "startTime": 67.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "「効能は、冷え性、神経痛、肩こりなどに\n効果がありま～す」……なんてね",
      "startTime": 76.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "温泉が気持ち良くて、つい長風呂しちゃうわ\nなんだか頭がぼんやりして……のぼせちゃったかも",
      "startTime": 86.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2866.6666666999986,
          "startTime": 84.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11266.666666700004,
          "startTime": 97.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君も\n今頃は温泉に入ってるのかしら……",
      "startTime": 94.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "いつもお世話になってるお礼に\n背中を流してあげるのもいいかもしれないわね……",
      "startTime": 100.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4000,
          "startTime": 104.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "「えっ、遙子さん！？　どうしてここに！？」",
      "startTime": 104.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "「ふふふ、びっくりした？\n今日は日頃の感謝を込めて君の背中を流してあげるわ」",
      "startTime": 110.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 108
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4866.666666699999,
          "startTime": 115.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "「えっ！　ま、待って下さい……」",
      "startTime": 115.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "「ほら、じっとして。そんなに動いたら洗えないでしょ\nもっとリラックスして……ね？」……ふふふ",
      "startTime": 124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……何考えてんだか。顔が火照ってきちゃった\nのぼせる前に上がろうっと",
      "startTime": 135.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳で、凄くいいお湯だったわ\n気持ち良過ぎてのぼせそうになっちゃった",
      "startTime": 144.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスと入浴したのに、一人で温泉を満喫して\n全然交流してないじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 151.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "だって、そもそも話をする機会がなかったのよ",
      "startTime": 154.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "すぐ喧嘩になるから、スリクスさんは出来るだけ\n喋らないようにしようってことになって……",
      "startTime": 161.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "おかげでみんな、温泉に入ってる間\nずっと黙り込んでたんだから",
      "startTime": 166.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "今夜はずっとあの調子だと思うと気が重いわね",
      "startTime": 169.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……これがプライベートの旅行だったら\n気楽に温泉を楽しめたのに",
      "startTime": 177.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはプライベートで\n温泉旅行に行ったりするんですか？",
      "startTime": 182.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "全く行ってないかな……\nでも、大学の友達は彼氏と温泉旅行をしたらしくて……",
      "startTime": 187.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
